6. Advanced Topics
==================


Deduplication: Store only unique file chunks to save space.
Delta Sync: Only upload/download changed parts of files.
Offline Support: Queue changes and sync when online.
Collaboration: Real-time editing and conflict resolution.
Monitoring & Analytics: Track usage, errors, and performance.